.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/checklist.md:23:| **[P1]** | Required | Must verify or record an operator-approved deferral |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/checklist.md:24:| **[P2]** | Optional | May defer with an explicit reason |
