.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md-138-### Implementation
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md-139-
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md-140-**What changes**:
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md:141:- P0: `ENV-REFERENCE.md` gains the flag entry; the verify harness gains drift-vs-breakage classification and a per-hub serving-status readout.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md:142:- P1: a drift-detection CI job plus the enforced rule that editing a hub's routing inputs re-mints its manifest in the same change.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md:143:- P2 to P4: a canary env profile, the data-driven eligibility rule (ADR-002), then the staged hub-by-hub default flip.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md-144-
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md-145-**How to roll back**: Nothing in this phase changes runtime behavior, so there is nothing to roll back here. Across the program, `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING=0` restores legacy serving fleet-wide, and each per-hub flip retains a byte-identical prior manifest for a byte-exact per-hub revert.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md-146-
--
