.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-192-
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-193-### Fallback correctness
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-194-- Hub with no manifest (a freshly created skill, pre-`013`): resolves to the legacy sentinel; routing unchanged — backward-compat by construction.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md:195:- Hub with a stale manifest (config edited, not re-minted): live hash ≠ minted digest ⇒ legacy sentinel; P1 CI fails re-mint-required.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-196-
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-197-### Observability boundaries
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md:198:- Drifted hub vs broken resolver: both currently read identically; P0 observability must separate "degraded/expected (drift)" from "broken (error)".
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-199-- All-legacy fleet under flag-on: a valid state (e.g. every hub mid-edit), must read as degraded, not failed.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-200-
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-201-### Kill-switch
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md:202:- `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING=0` after P4 default-on: must fully restore legacy serving fleet-wide, documented as the kill-switch, not an incidental default.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-203-
