.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/implementation-summary.md:36:Lane C will gain a deterministic parity module around the existing scorer. For eligible route-gold scenarios it will preserve the legacy replay, invoke the real public compiled front door with a child-only flag-on environment, normalize both routing results, run the same gold evaluator twice, and require mutual routing equality.
