.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/implementation-summary.md:67:| Exercise the public front door in a child process | Tests the real flag and serving gates and prevents parent environment leakage. |
