.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:78:- **Eligibility/status adapter**: decides whether compiled parity is required and why a sentinel occurred.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md-79-- **Compiled child-process adapter**: runs the public front door with an isolated flag-on environment.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:80:- **Normalizer**: maps legacy intents and compiled qualified targets through `mode-registry.json` into action/selection/ordered targets.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:81:- **Parity evaluator**: calls frozen route-gold evaluation twice and compares routing projections.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:82:- **Report gate**: aggregates row results without changing D1-D5 values.
