.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/spec.md-2-title: "Feature Specification: Lane C Compiled-Routing Benchmark Alignment"
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/spec.md:3:description: "Plan the Lane C harness changes that exercise the compiled router with SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING=1, compare its normalized routing decisions with legacy router replay and the same authored route gold, and classify manifest drift separately from compiled-path breakage without editing the three frozen scorer files."
