    75	
    76	| Check | Result |
    77	|-------|--------|
    78	| Current-state source inspection | Confirmed: parent generator and templates have no compiled-routing awareness |
    79	| Directive rendering tests | Planned |
    80	| Legacy no-manifest test | Planned |
    81	| Ready fresh-manifest test | Planned |
    82	| Mint/freshness failure matrix | Planned |
    83	| Standalone and existing parent regression suite | Planned |
    84	| Strict skill-package and spec-folder validation | Planned spec command: `bash .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/spec/validate.sh .opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment --strict` |
    85	<!-- /ANCHOR:verification -->
    86	
    87	---
    88	
    89	<!-- ANCHOR:limitations -->
    90	## Known Limitations
    91	
    92	1. **Ready mode depends on P3 interfaces that do not exist yet.** This packet cannot truthfully select a manifest location or eligibility result before those interfaces stabilize.
    93	2. **Current runtime discovery is limited to established hubs.** A new hub cannot become operationally compiled-ready until P3 removes that fixed discovery boundary.
    94	3. **Existing hubs are not migrated by this phase.** The generator affects new explicit runs only.
    95	4. **A mint-failure retention policy remains open.** The operator must choose whether failed ready output stays as a diagnostic legacy scaffold or remains staged outside the final target.
    96	<!-- /ANCHOR:limitations -->
