.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:43:- The user needs manual validation scenarios. Use `create-manual-testing-playbook`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:80:This is a nested workflow packet under `sk-doc`. It carries its own `SKILL.md`, `README.md`, `references/`, `assets/`, and `changelog/`, but it must not define a packet-local `graph-metadata.json`; advisor identity lives at the `sk-doc` hub root.
